Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.48,0:00:09.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Excellent.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.05,0:00:12.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No hemorrhaging or ischemia found.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.00,0:00:16.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No major change in red blood cells, \Nwhite blood cells, or hematocrit.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But your pulse is a bit on the rapid side.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.91,0:00:23.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you under any stress, Minnie C. Tachibana?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.17,0:00:24.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Not especially.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.78,0:00:28.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tired of all these physical exams?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.45,0:00:29.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.79,0:00:32.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,My husband enjoyed physical exams, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.86,0:00:35.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,He said it was like being in an amusement park.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.82,0:00:38.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.31,0:00:39.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, next is...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.22,0:00:43.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.93,0:00:50.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's finish another time.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kitou{-san} wants to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.09,0:00:55.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.15,0:02:40.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Doesn't Mount Fuji look beautiful today?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. It certainly does.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's just like the day I first came here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You know, to tell the truth, I was quite worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.05,0:02:58.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When I heard a former US Marine Corps \Nsecond lieutenant was coming,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I expected someone scary...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it ended up being \Nsomeone like you, Tachibana{-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please feel free to call me "Minnie C."
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.92,0:03:12.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's how my husband introduced\N me to his friends and family.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll do that, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.46,0:03:18.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You look wonderful in a kimono, Minnie C.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you often visit Japan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.23,0:03:22.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.11,0:03:26.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I first saw Mount Fuji when \NI flew over it on my honeymoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,My husband was so excited!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.83,0:03:29.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.44,0:03:33.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,He loved Japanese culture more than anything,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.87,0:03:37.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,so when I wear a kimono, I feel as if he's near me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you see it, darling?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.57,0:03:48.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.78,0:03:57.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I want more.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll go buy some more.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.21,0:04:09.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So your name is Sana{-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.34,0:04:13.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you the lady who talked \Nto me at the research facility?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,but we have met recently.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.09,0:04:19.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I was asked to handle the pigs.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Right, over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What will they do with them?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They'll be cared for at a special facility.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.78,0:04:34.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The people there will probably do a few tests,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,but they won't harm the pigs at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.64,0:04:37.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Tests?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.97,0:04:42.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They're very special pigs \Ncreated by your power, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.98,0:04:45.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You know about me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Where did this pig come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.27,0:04:57.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.47,0:05:01.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, it's alive, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.62,0:05:05.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What would happen if I used \Nmy power to get rid of it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.93,0:05:20.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.14,0:05:24.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You know those long cylinders we always use, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Right, I'd like nine, if possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can we do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.92,0:05:33.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Great, I'll send someone to get them now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Cylinders? For the flowers?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The things like vases?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.95,0:05:39.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chinatsu! Ichirou!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.97,0:05:42.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.29,0:05:46.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I never knew those were provided by the florist.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.41,0:05:49.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm no expert, but can't you use something else?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Everything's decided through prior discussion.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.90,0:05:55.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't just change things like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.30,0:06:01.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I need you to go to Sakaki{-san}'s place \Nin Kokubunji and pick up the stuff listed.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Take care of them, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just leave them to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,How's it going on your end?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm still analyzing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This ability-user has a complex signal.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.52,0:06:25.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Her name is Sana{-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.56,0:06:32.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll keep analyzing Sana{-chan}'s pattern!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.30,0:06:36.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When I see them like this, pigs are pretty adorable.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.71,0:06:37.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.65,0:06:38.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.90,0:06:41.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see one that looked a bit different?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Was there one like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I believe you have something to say to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's apologize together.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, Sana{-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.74,0:06:57.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It wasn't on purpose.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask if it was on purpose!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't a simple apology come first? Well?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,L-Listen, Grandpa...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.56,0:07:10.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan} really didn't do it deliberately.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I realize that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.66,0:07:16.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But whether she meant any harm, \Nthe fact is that she did this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I told you not to use those \Nweird powers anymore, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.22,0:07:24.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,One wrong move, and "sorry" \Nisn't gonna cut it anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.82,0:07:25.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Bu—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.34,0:07:28.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can't you even keep a promise?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.11,0:07:28.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,B-B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.76,0:07:35.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't on purpose!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.52,0:07:38.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to the research facility for my...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't cry!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,C'mon, take it easy, old man!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't be so touchy all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And toward a little girl, at your age.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.54,0:07:53.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Little girl, my name's Naitou Ryu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm this scary old man's friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.48,0:07:59.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Know what "Ryu" means? \NIt means "dragon" in Japanese.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Pretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not done—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just hold up a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.47,0:08:11.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm one of the guys who've been\N chasing the baddies who held you prisoner.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.74,0:08:19.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So it's also our job to make\N sure that you're kept safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.65,0:08:22.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And on that note, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.94,0:08:28.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We can't know when those guys\N will try to take you away again.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So, to be sure we always know where you are,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.25,0:08:33.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to wear a homing device.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.72,0:08:34.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.78,0:08:37.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't like it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Then, how about this one?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't seem like a bad person, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.78,0:08:46.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll put it on for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not a bad guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She said the same about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.51,0:09:00.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I guess she likes it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sanae, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.51,0:09:10.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Already?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.77,0:09:13.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Shall I send someone to buy something?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I want that juice from before.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.87,0:09:17.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Sana{-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.87,0:09:20.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.73,0:09:21.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You want some, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can I? Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.74,0:09:24.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.91,0:09:25.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.98,0:09:36.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're already there?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for moving so fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll transfer to the mission vehicle and stand by.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.25,0:09:45.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ready for your order anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.49,0:09:48.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait just a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to you soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.87,0:10:12.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that lady coming here?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You mean Minnie C?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She'll be nearby, but I don't think she'll join us.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't like her.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.43,0:10:23.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But I think she's very nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's always smiling.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't smiling all the time
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,the same as never smiling?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're rather perceptive, Kureo.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ah, in Iraq?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.48,0:10:41.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, while defusing a bomb.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And after her husband died,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.42,0:10:47.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,she suffered from insomnia and was\N on the verge of being discharged.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.98,0:10:52.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But then, after dreaming that her\N husband's arms were embracing her,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,her condition immediately stabilized.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And that's when she became a Dream of Alice?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.87,0:10:58.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In any case, she's an intriguing sample.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.93,0:11:07.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There have been very few cases \Nof a living being turning into a card.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.89,0:11:12.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if it's only one part of that being.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen, Minnie C.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes? What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.25,0:11:44.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I think I'm happier now \Nthan I've ever been in my life.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will sound silly.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.58,0:12:12.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I never feared death until I met you,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Minnie C.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.49,0:12:30.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You have some on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.54,0:12:36.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Watching you is making me hungry, Sana{-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Are these for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You want any?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.36,0:12:48.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you interested in becoming \Na member of Zouroku{-san}'s family?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.80,0:12:58.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.96,0:13:01.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Chill out, buddy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You'd have to make arrangements!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Like tableware and futons—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.04,0:13:08.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.26,0:13:11.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The agreement was to take her to \Na safe place, where she'd be cared for!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but just think about it...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.32,0:13:17.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is a kid who gets into car races\N with supernatural powers in town.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who else is gonna take her in?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just what do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.73,0:13:26.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen, I just want to leave her in \Nthe hands of a good, responsible guardian.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll personally arrange bodyguards \Nand everything, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You'd damn well better!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.22,0:13:34.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Besides, old man,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.22,0:13:36.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,what this girl needs is a family.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.04,0:13:41.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,A warm home where she can \Neat good food and sleep safely.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's never known that kind of ordinary happiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,"Ordinary happiness"?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.40,0:13:49.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.12,0:13:53.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When you talk about stuff like that,\N there's always an ulterior motive!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I've gotta hand it to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You know me well.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Still, just do this for me...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.57,0:14:03.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They want her to experience \Na normal lifestyle as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who does?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Weren't you sort of considering this, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.91,0:14:12.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's how you are. I know you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.89,0:14:19.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you ended up living with us, what would you do?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.14,0:14:25.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.67,0:14:29.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I think I'd be kind of happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And you, Zouroku?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.50,0:14:36.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you not want me in your house?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.95,0:14:39.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Look, before we get to that,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.64,0:14:42.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,you still haven't said something important to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You know there's something you have to say first.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,B-Bathroom!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.18,0:14:51.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.05,0:14:54.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No, really. I gotta pee!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}did{\i0} drink a lot of juice.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, Sana{-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your hair will get in the way like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.22,0:15:08.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can you use the bathroom by yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I can do anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, you're all set.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you would, Minnie C.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.82,0:15:27.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.73,0:15:30.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,A member of Zouroku's family, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.38,0:15:33.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'd live in that house, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.02,0:15:37.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll apologize to Zouroku after this.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Guess I have no choice!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I guess I have no choice!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan}, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The transmitter's moving!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yamada, where is she?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make a right 300 meters ahead, \Nand then go straight for 500 more.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naitou{-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.51,0:16:14.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They got us!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.71,0:16:18.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They rewrote the toilet's location!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.86,0:16:31.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When she's like this, she looks like an ordinary child.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well done, darling.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks for always being there.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I have Sana{-chan}'s signal, ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.15,0:16:47.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.85,0:16:51.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's really weak, but the pattern is a match.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.00,0:16:51.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.03,0:16:56.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The system is still unstable, so I can't pinpoint it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.69,0:16:59.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The GPS was for this, but now...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ma'am! Her signal's gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.21,0:17:05.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Contact Naitou{-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.89,0:17:08.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Check all area surveillance cameras at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger that!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.49,0:17:25.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh? You've already perked up,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Red Queen?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.57,0:17:32.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We gave you enough to knock\N out an adult for half a day.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.44,0:17:36.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of monster are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.25,0:17:43.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I am Minnie C. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.46,0:17:46.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I've come from the research facility to collect you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.56,0:17:53.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.11,0:17:54.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's happening?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.28,0:17:55.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.82,0:18:00.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Being restrained by so much strength\N that you cannot move at all
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.21,0:18:02.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,is rather alarming, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In the military, I had that experience.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.12,0:18:08.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That won't work.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.01,0:18:14.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you just stay quiet, we will arrive soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.06,0:18:15.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's go home together.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wonderland?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.61,0:18:21.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to show it to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.19,0:18:34.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just what are the Dreams of Alice?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, rather than a gift from the heavens,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.51,0:18:43.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,they're actually an illness, \Nor a bug in the workings of this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.35,0:18:47.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's what some people say.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.38,0:18:49.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.87,0:18:53.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I don't think it matters.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if they're demons,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.27,0:18:59.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,if they can be used for a purpose,\N then it's human nature to do so.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That is why I've come here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.94,0:19:04.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's great to hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.26,0:19:15.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What I'm about to show you may \Nshed some light on those demons.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.18,0:19:19.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.46,0:19:24.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,part of the facility underground\N was rewritten into a mess,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.27,0:19:27.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,and an impossibly huge space appeared.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that a relay antenna?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.66,0:19:35.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We tried releasing drones\N to observe the space inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.53,0:19:36.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But it didn't work.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.26,0:19:41.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Anything in here that she dislikes is destroyed.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,"She"?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.95,0:19:48.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It seems that she won't harm humans, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.28,0:19:50.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I've brought a visitor.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.69,0:19:55.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Turn on the light.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.18,0:20:02.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I need your data in order to learn\N what she really is, Minnie C.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We call her
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.14,0:20:12.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,the Red Queen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.93,0:20:20.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This ridiculous spectacle
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.21,0:20:25.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,is an inexhaustible collection of cards\N she's created from her Mirror Gate.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.50,0:20:29.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But for Dreams of Alice, cards are...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, each only has one.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.64,0:20:35.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And getting the power they want isn't guaranteed.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But she is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.50,0:20:44.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In this Wonderland,\N everything she wishes for becomes reality.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Anything she can imagine
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.19,0:20:50.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,can come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.16,0:20:55.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you could obtain this power for yourself,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.55,0:20:57.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,what would you wish for?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I shall explain what's happening now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.06,0:21:16.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Currently,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.57,0:21:21.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,you're in a vehicle moving at 100 kph, \Non a road you don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you were thrown outside right now,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.43,0:21:27.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,you would either crash into the ground \Nor into another vehicle, and you'd die.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.85,0:21:31.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And if I apply just a little more strength,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.21,0:21:34.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,your neck will break, and you'll die.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.05,0:21:37.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.59,0:21:38.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you just imagine it now?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.49,0:21:42.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you struggle or disobey me,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,you will die.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.62,0:21:54.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until I met you, I'd never feared death,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Minnie C.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.49,0:21:59.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I would do absolutely anything
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.39,0:22:01.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,to see him again,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.21,0:22:05.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Red Queen.
